Package scriptmanager.window_interface.Sequence_Analysis

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DNAShapefromBEDOutput
    Graphical window for displaying the DNA shape scores and charts for the set of input BED intervals.
    DNAShapefromBEDWindow
    Graphical interface window for calculating various aspects of DNA shape across a set of BED intervals by calling a script implemented in the scripts package.
    DNAShapefromFASTAOutput
    Graphical window for displaying the DNA shape scores and charts for the set of input FASTA sequences.
    DNAShapefromFASTAWindow
    Graphical interface window for calculating various aspects of DNA shape across a set of FASTA sequences by calling the methods implemented in the scripts package.
    FASTAExtractOutput
    Graphical window for displaying progress as genomic sequence is extracted from a set of coordinates.
    FASTAExtractWindow
    Graphical interface window for extracting the genomic sequence of a set of BED intervals by calling a script implemented in the scripts package.
    RandomizeFASTAWindow
    Graphical interface window for randomizing sequences (shuffling nucleotides) in a FASTA file by calling the methods implemented in the scripts package.
    SearchMotifOutput
    Graphical window for displaying progress as genome sequences are searched for a given motif.
    SearchMotifWindow
    Graphical interface window for searching for genomic motif sequences by calling a script implemented in the scripts package.
